Module\\n```\\n\\n#### Data Flow\\n1. The application starts up and calls the `load_tasks` function to populate the task list from a JSON file.\\n2. The user interacts with the CLI to execute commands (add, view, complete, delete tasks).\\n3. Each command triggers the respective function in the Task Management Module.\\n4. Changes to tasks are saved back to the JSON file via the `save_tasks` function on application exit.\\n\\n### Next Steps\\n- Write the design document in the knowledge base for future reference and implementation guidance.\\n- Return control back to the Project Manager once documentation is complete.\\n\\nI will now draft and write the design document in the knowledge base.\",\"type\":\"ThoughtEvent\"},{\"id\":\"c52d27ba-52e1-4ddd-a1d6-22557a110b20\",\"source\":\"Architect\",\"models_usage\":{\"prompt_tokens\":1416,\"completion_tokens\":1228},\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T07:17:27.670525Z\",\"content\":[{\"id\":\"call_d7rDDJP44QlrMrNlGk5HjBhW\",\"arguments\":\"{\\\"path\\\":\\\"cli_todo_app_architecture.md\\\",\\\"content\\\":\\\"# Architecture Design for CLI Todo App with JSON\\\\n\\\\n## Overview\\\\nThe CLI Todo application allows users to manage tasks via a command-line interface, utilizing JSON for data storage. Below is a proposed architecture outlining the essential components, their responsibilities, and the data flow.\\\\n\\\\n## Core Components\\\\n\\\\n1. **Task Management Module**\\\\n   - **Responsibilities:**\\\\n     - Create a new task.\\\\n     - View all tasks.\\\\n     - Mark a task as completed.\\\\n     - Delete a task.\\\\n   - **Key Functions:**\\\\n     - `add_task(description: str)`: Adds a new task with a description.\\\\n     - `view_tasks()`: Lists all current tasks, including their status.\\\\n     - `mark_task_done(task_id: int)`: Updates a task to mark it as completed.\\\\n     - `delete_task(task_id: int)`: Removes a task from the list.\\\\n\\\\n2. **JSON Handling Module**\\\\n   - **Responsibilities:**\\\\n     - Load tasks from a JSON file at the application's startup.\\\\n     - Save the current list of tasks to a JSON file before the application closes.\\\\n   - **Key Functions:**\\\\n     - `load_tasks(filename: str)`: Reads tasks from a specified JSON file.\\\\n     - `save_tasks(filename: str)`: Writes the current tasks to a specified JSON file.\\\\n\\\\n3. **CLI Interface Module**\\\\n   - **Responsibilities:**\\\\n     - Handle user inputs through the command line.\\\\n     - Display outputs back to the user.\\\\n   - **Key Functions:**\\\\n     - `run_cli()`: Main loop for the command-line interface which processes user commands.\\\\n\\\\n## Data Model\\\\n- **Task Structure (JSON Object)**\\\\n```json\\\\n{\\\\n  \\\\\\\"tasks\\\\\\\": [\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\": 1,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Buy groceries\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"done\\\\\\\": false\\\\n    },\\\\n    {\\\\n      \\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\": 2,\\\\n      \\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\"Read a book\\\\\\\",\\\\n      \\\\\\\"done\\\\\\\": true\\\\n    }\\\\n  ]\\\\n}\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n## Project Structure\\\\n```plaintext\\\\ncli_todo_app/\\\\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 main.py               # Entry point for the application\\\\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 task_manager.py       # Contains Task Management Module\\\\n\u251c\u2500\u2500 json_handler.py       # Contains JSON Handling Module\\\\n\u2514\u2500\u2500 cli_interface.py      # Contains CLI Interface Module\\\\n```\\\\n\\\\n## Data Flow\\\\n1. The application starts up and calls the `load_tasks` function to populate the task list from a JSON file.\\\\n2. The user interacts with the CLI to execute commands (add, view, complete, delete tasks).\\\\n3. Each command triggers the respective function in the Task Management Module.\\\\n4. Changes to tasks are saved back to the JSON file via the `save_tasks` function on application exit.\\\"}\",\"name\":\"docs_write_file\"}],\"type\":\"ToolCallRequestEvent\"},{\"id\":\"b9e9e29f-258d-4a14-aea1-3e9d851ca518\",\"source\":\"Architect\",\"models_usage\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T07:17:27.708258Z\",\"content\":[{\"content\":\"Successfully wrote to data/knowledge_base/cli_todo_app_architecture.md\",\"name\":\"docs_write_file\",\"call_id\":\"call_d7rDDJP44QlrMrNlGk5HjBhW\",\"is_error\":false}],\"type\":\"ToolCallExecutionEvent\"}]},\"name\":\"Architect\"}", "sender": "Architect_fb0e91c0-ca3a-41c5-afc4-e3055aa83102/fb0e91c0-ca3a-41c5-afc4-e3055aa83102", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
