 {"role": "user", "name": "Engineer", "content": "Input validation error: 'repo_path' is a required property"}, {"role": "user", "name": "Engineer", "content": "Input validation error: 'repo_path' is a required property\nInput validation error: 'repo_path' is a required property\nInput validation error: 'repo_path' is a required property\nInput validation error: 'repo_path' is a required property"}, {"role": "user", "name": "Engineer", "content": "Transferred to ProjectManager, adopting the role of ProjectManager immediately."}, {"role": "assistant", "tool_calls": [{"id": "call_dKGQo5Ew5IejT4HLdhwDykc4", "function": {"arguments": "{\"path\":\"data/project_board/cli_todo_app_code_review.md\",\"content\":\"# Code Review for CLI Todo App\\n\\n## Code Files Implemented:\\n- Models: `data/workspace/models/todo.js`\\n- Controllers: `data/workspace/controllers/todoController.js`\\n- Routes: `data/workspace/routes/todoRoutes.js`\\n- Main Entry: `data/workspace/index.js`\\n\\n## Issues Noted:\\n- Continuous input validation errors regarding 'repo_path'. This needs to be addressed.\\n\\n**Status: TO DO**\\n\\n**Links:** Implementation Document: [Implementation Tasks](data/project_board/cli_todo_app_implementation.md)\"}", "name": "board_write_file"}, "type": "function"}], "content": "The Engineering team has made significant progress in creating the files and directory structure for the CLI Todo App. However, it seems there were continuous input validation errors related to a required property: 'repo_path'. \n\n### Next Steps:\n\n1. **Code Review**: Before we can proceed, I will need to initiate a code review to ensure that the implemented code adheres to best practices and resolves any errors.\n\n#### Ticket Status:\n- I'll create a code review ticket that references the implementation, and then I will delegate the code review task to the CodeReviewer.\n\nI will now create a ticket for the code review."}, {"content": "Successfully wrote to data/project_board/cli_todo_app_cod